vice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["checkoutservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "frontend-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T23:10:09Z to 2025-06-20T23:35:09Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 23:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-20 23:35:09+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["checkoutservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "frontend-2"]}, "log_analysis_findings": "根据收集的日志，我发现系统的错误情况与以下问题相关：\n\n### 提取的关键信息：\n- **问题关键词**:\n  - `transport: Error while dialing`\n  - `connection refused`\n  - `failed to complete the order`\n  - `rpc error: code = Unavailable`\n- **异常服务**:\n  - 日志集中出现了对 `shippingservice` 的调用失败，错误出现在调用 `shippingservice` 的前端 `frontend` 服务中。\n  - 日志包含 `desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused\"`。\n- **日志频次和分布**:\n  - 错误日志主要来源于 `frontend` 服务的多个 Pod，包括 `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`, 和 `frontend-0`。\n  - 常见模式是 Frontend 服务报告调用 `shippingservice` 失败的两类问题：`connection refused` 和 `transport is closing`。\n\n### 主要故障模式推测：\n- **DNS 或连接错误**:\n  - 出现关键词 `transport: Error while dialing` 和 `connection refused` 是典型特征，表明 `frontend` 与目标服务之间在特定时间窗口存在连接问题，可能是由于网络错误或目标端口配置问题。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport: Error while dialing\", \"connection refused\", \"rpc error: code = Unavailable\", \"failed to complete the order\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend 服务调用 shippingservice 上的请求失败，提示连接被拒绝 (connection refused)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"示例日志: 'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"日志表明 frontend 试图发起 RPC 请求时可能由于暂时性网络错误或者 phía shippingservice 的网络配置问题导致失败。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"示例日志: 'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据 UUID 为 5d022708-414 的故障分析，以下是主要发现的异常:\n\n### 异常指标\n从故障数据分析中，异常指标包括以下几点，已选择绝对值变化最大的 Top 3 指标：\n1. `node_memory_usage_rate` — `aiops-k8s-01` Node 在故障期间内发生显著内存使用率变化。\n2. `rrt_max` — Service 的最大响应时间出现了显著变化，尤其在 `frontend` 和其他服务中。\n3. `client_error_ratio` — 多个服务，包括 `shippingservice` 和 `cartservice` 客户端错误率显著增高。\n\n### 具体发现\n扫描数据表明：\n- Node `aiops-k8s-01` 的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 变化显著，可能是引发多个服务异常的根因。\n- `frontend` 服务在 `aiops-k8s-08` 上运行，存在显著的 `rrt_max` 增长问题，这表明其可能与 Node 上的 Pod 资源争用相关。\n- `shippingservice` 和 `cartservice` 的 Pod 在故障期间生成了异常量的客户端错误，然而这些 Pod 关联的 Node (`aiops-k8s-01`) 也报告了异常的内存使用问题。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-01\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion causing multiple service errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate from 30.26% reduced to 27.87%, indicating possible memory shortage\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"High rrt_max indicating potential response time bottleneck\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend rrt_max shifted from 255295 to 103809 during fault period\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client error rates increased, aligning with node memory issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Detected client_error_ratio from 0 increased to 57\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现为进一步调查提供了初步证据，建议在之后的阶段针对 `aiops-k8s-01` 和受影响的服务进行深入地分析，识别确切的资源争用和错误根因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据UUID相关数据的初步扫描，以下是任务异常期间的调用链和状态分析结果：\n\n### 说明：\n1. 调用链数据结合延迟异常和状态错误进行整理。\n2. 检查显著异常的调用环节。\n3. 识别错误状态和最有可能影响系统的节点。\n\n### 分析结果 (见`detected_trace_keys`):\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"connection_refused\", \"frontend->shippingservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection_refused and repeated RPC error with Unavailable status during ship quoting.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Transport Error and anomaly_avg_duration drop drastically to 126~144ms with connection refused.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Propagated error from shippingservice caused delays and failures in checkout transactions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Shipping quotes failing in checkout process with reduced throughput and Unavailable status.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis (cartservice)\",\n      \"reason\": \"Major latency spike during redis HMSET operations.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"anomaly_avg_duration jumped from ~1.3s to 30s.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 核心异常和延迟链条：\n1. **ShippingService**：\n   - 调用链：`frontend->shippingservice`，`checkoutservice->shippingservice`\n   - 状态码组合：`HTTP status code 14; Connection error: Unavailable`.\n   - 频次：高达 **262 次** 以上，导致运输报价失败。\n   - 异常耗时时间葬影响链：减少到 **126ms~144ms**，显示`Fast Fail`信号，可能是因目标RPC服务未正常。\n\n2. **Propagated to CheckoutService**:\n   - 调用链：`frontend->checkoutservice`, 表面上为ShippingService未能返回 (失败消息传播)\n   - 信息：所有 Checkout step 消息抛出 cascade API Exception。\n   \n3. **Secondary Issue Identified: REDIS 服务 Backup延缓**\n   ---\n    JSON_USERS_ROUTECLARITIES $RED_MODEL"}
